  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2016-12-01T05:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Drinking Water Affordability Act of 2016\n\nThis bill amends the Safe Drinking Water Act to revise requirements concerning national primary drinking water regulations, including by:\n\n removing a requirement that the Environmental Protection Agency maintain, or provide greater, protection of human health when revising those regulations; extending the repayment schedule for loans from the drinking water state revolving funds (SRF); removing certain SRF matching fund requirement for states; authorizing states to protect public drinking water source areas; and removing federal reporting requirements if state or local requirements are at least equally stringent as federal requirements."
  }, 
